return ['domain'=>NULL,'plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','language'=>'zh','pot-creation-date'=>'2026-01-07 15:17-0600','po-revision-date'=>'2026-01-07 15:17-0600','translation-revision-date'=>'2026-01-07 15:17-0600','project-id-version'=>'ICS Calendar','x-generator'=>'Poedit 3.8','messages'=>['%1$s is currently %2$spaused%3$s, and is not serving calendars on front end pages. You can resume serving calendars under the %4$sUtilities%5$s tab %6$shere%7$s.'=>'%1$s当前处于%2$s暂停%3$s状态，前端页面暂不提供日历服务。您可通过%4$s实用工具%5$s选项卡%6$s在此处%7$s重新启用日历服务。','%1$sYou are running ICS Calendar in a WordPress Playground implementation.%2$s Because ICS Calendar is intended to run on a web server, some features may be unavailable or may not function properly.'=>'%1$s您正在WordPress Playground环境中运行ICS日历。%2$s由于ICS日历旨在运行于Web服务器，部分功能可能无法使用或无法正常运作。','%1$sYour site is currently using a UTC offset-based timezone setting.%2$s This can produce time display errors in the %3$s plugin in locations that observe Daylight Saving Time. Please %4$schange your timezone setting%5$s to the city nearest your location, in the same timezone, for proper time display. See our %6$sdocumentation%7$s for additional information on this issue.'=>'%1$s您的网站当前采用基于UTC偏移量的时间区域设置。%2$s在实行夏令时的地区，这可能导致%3$s插件出现时间显示错误。请%4$s将时间区域设置%5$s更改为与您所在位置最近且时区相同的城市，以确保时间显示准确。有关此问题的更多信息，请参阅我们的%6$s文档%7$s。','Important! Your %1$s configuration appears to be exceeding source calendar provider rate limits.'=>'重要提示！您的%1$s配置似乎已超过源日历提供商的速率限制。','If your calendars are not loading properly, please review your %1$s settings and usage:'=>'如果您的日历无法正常加载，请检查您的%1$s设置和使用情况：','Do not use %1$s in your shortcodes. This feature is intended for troubleshooting only, and should not be left on permanently.'=>'请勿在短代码中使用 %1$s。此功能仅用于故障排除，不应长期启用。','Increase the %1$s %2$sTransient (cache) expiration%3$s setting to %4$s43200%5$s (12 hours) or greater, to reduce the frequency of requests to the provider. (See note below.)'=>'将%1$s %2$s临时（缓存）过期时间%3$s设置为%4$s43200%5$s（12小时）或更长，以降低向提供商发送请求的频率。（参见下方注释。）','Avoid including a large number of feeds (10 or more) from the same provider in a single %1$s shortcode.'=>'避免在单个%1$s短代码中包含来自同一提供商的大量订阅源（10个或更多）。','Temporarily pause ICS Calendar on your front-end pages using the %1$sPause Calendars%2$s utility. (24-48 hours is recommended.)'=>'使用%1$s暂停日历%2$s工具，在前端页面暂时暂停ICS日历服务。（建议暂停24-48小时。）','%1$s includes built-in caching, specifically to improve performance and avoid exceeding provider rate limits. Circumventing this caching with a very low %2$sreload%3$s setting may trigger a temporary block on your web server IP address, or possibly on your entire hosting network, by the calendar provider.'=>'%1$s内置缓存功能，旨在提升性能并避免超出服务商速率限制。若通过极低%2$sreload%3$s设置绕过此缓存机制，可能会触发日历服务商对您网站服务器IP地址（甚至整个托管网络）实施临时封禁。','After making the recommended changes, please allow up to 24 hours for your calendar provider to remove any temporary blocks on your IP address. If you find that the problem persists, please use our %1$ssupport request form%2$s to contact us, and be sure to include your %3$ssystem report%4$s.'=>'完成建议的修改后，请等待最多24小时，以便日历提供商解除对您IP地址的临时封锁。若问题仍未解决，请通过我们的%1$s支持请求表单%2$s联系我们，并务必附上您的%3$s系统报告%4$s。','Note: Set the %1$sTransient (cache) expiration%2$s as large as possible, considering how frequently event information in your calendar is typically updated. %3$s Remember that you can use the %4$sClear Cached Calendar Data%5$s utility to manually clear the cache at any time, if needed.'=>'注意：请将%1$s临时缓存过期时间%2$s设置为尽可能长的值，同时需考虑日历中事件信息的通常更新频率。%3$s请记住，您可随时使用%4$s清除缓存日历数据%5$s工具手动清除缓存。','%1$sPlease note:%2$s %3$s version 10.6 changes the default options for several shortcode settings. In order to maintain consistency, these new defaults are %4$snot%5$s enabled when upgrading from an earlier version. If you would like to learn more about the changes please read our %6$sblog post%7$s, or to switch to the new defaults, turn on the %8$s option on the %9$s settings%10$s page.'=>'%1$s请注意：%2$s %3$s 10.6 版本更改了多个短代码设置的默认选项。为保持一致性，从旧版本升级时这些新默认值%4$s不会%5$s自动启用。 若需了解变更详情，请参阅我们的%6$s博客文章%7$s；如需启用新默认设置，请在%9$s设置%10$s页面开启%8$s选项。','Use new parameter defaults (v.10.6)'=>'使用新的参数默认值（v.10.6）','%1$sPlease note:%2$s %3$s version 11.0 streamlines the way ICS feed URLs are retrieved. This change uses a standard built-in WordPress function, so it should be fully compatible with all existing installations. If you encounter any new issues after upgrading to version 11 or later, please visit the %4$sWordPress Support Forums%5$s for assistance.'=>'%1$s请注意：%2$s %3$s 11.0版本优化了ICS订阅源URL的获取方式。此变更采用WordPress内置标准函数实现，因此应与所有现有安装完全兼容。若升级至11.0及以上版本后遇到新问题，请访问%4$sWordPress支持论坛%5$s寻求帮助。','%1$sPlease note:%2$s %3$s version 11.5.14.2 introduces a new, more secure method for handling calendar parameters when loading via AJAX. Please clear any caching plugins you are using, to ensure that your calendars are loading properly with the new method.'=>'%1$s请注意：%2$s %3$s 版本 11.5.14.2 引入了一种更安全的新方法来处理通过 AJAX 加载日历参数。请清除您正在使用的任何缓存插件，以确保日历能通过新方法正确加载。','%1$sWelcome to %2$s version 12!%3$s Version 12.0 introduces additional troubleshooting tools, plus a number of performance improvements and interface refinements throughout. Please see the %4$schangelog%5$s for more details on this update.'=>'%1$s欢迎使用%2$s第12版！%3$s12.0版本新增了更多故障排除工具，同时全面优化了性能并完善了界面设计。有关本次更新的详细信息，请参阅%4$s变更日志%5$s。','Getting Started'=>'入门指南','Settings'=>'设置','Appearance'=>'外观','Utilities'=>'工具','System Report'=>'系统报告','Support'=>'支持','Upgrade to %1$s!'=>'升级至%1$s！','Show/hide all'=>'显示/隐藏全部','ICS file could not be retrieved or was empty. Please verify URL is correct, and check your php.ini configuration to verify either cURL or allow_url_fopen is available. If you are using spaces to delimit multiple URLs, you may also wish to try using the pipe character instead. Affected URL:'=>'无法检索ICS文件或文件为空。请确认URL地址正确，并检查php.ini配置中是否启用了cURL或allow_url_fopen功能。若使用空格分隔多个URL，建议改用竖线分隔符。受影响的URL：','Hide past events'=>'隐藏过去的活动','Show past events'=>'显示过往事件','Contact:'=>'联系人:','Resources:'=>'相关资源','Click for more...'=>'点击查看更多...','Save to your calendar'=>'添加到日历','Cancelled'=>'已取消','The legacy parser option is deprecated and will be removed in a future update.'=>'旧版解析器选项已被弃用，将在未来的更新中移除。','Print'=>'打印','The "currentweek" shortcode attribute is deprecated. Please use view="week" in your shortcode instead.'=>'"currentweek" 短代码属性已弃用。请改用 view="week" 替代。','The "legendinline" shortcode attribute is deprecated. Please use legendstyle="inline" in your shortcode instead.'=>'"legendinline" 短代码属性已弃用。请改用 legendstyle="inline" 替代。','%1$s has %2$sresumed%3$s serving calendars on front end pages. If your site uses a caching plugin, you may need to clear the cache.'=>'%1$s已%2$s恢复%3$s在前端页面显示日历。若您的站点使用缓存插件，可能需要清除缓存。','%1$s has %2$spaused%3$s serving calendars on front end pages. If your site uses a caching plugin, you may need to clear the cache.'=>'%1$s已%2$s暂停%3$s在前端页面提供日历服务。若您的站点使用缓存插件，可能需要清除缓存。','Cleared %1$s %2$s transient(s).'=>'清除 %1$s %2$s 个瞬态。','No %1$s transients were found.'=>'%1$s 未發現任何瞬態現象。','All saved ICS feed URLs have been cleared.'=>'所有已保存的ICS源URL均已清除。','All %1$s settings have been reset to defaults, and saved ICS feed URLs have been cleared.'=>'所有%1$s设置均已重置为默认值，已保存的ICS源URL已被清除。','Your feed URL appears to contain HTTP Basic Authentication credentials. Try turning off the %1$s option under the %2$s tab above.'=>'您的订阅源网址似乎包含HTTP基本认证凭据。请尝试关闭上方%2$s选项卡下的%1$s选项。','Use legacy feed request method'=>'使用传统数据源请求方法','%1$sThis URL points to a file in your Media Library.%2$s While you should be able to use this URL in an %3$s shortcode, it will be a static snapshot of the calendar at the time the file was created, and will not reflect any future updates to the source calendar. Please see our %4$sUser Guide%5$s for instructions on obtaining your correct dynamic feed URL.'=>'%1$s此URL指向您媒体库中的文件。%2$s虽然您可以在%3$s短代码中使用该URL，但它仅为文件创建时日历的静态快照，不会反映源日历的后续更新。请参阅我们的%4$s用户指南%5$s，了解如何获取正确的动态源URL。','Error: Could not resolve IP address for %1$s.'=>'错误：无法解析 %1$s 的 IP 地址。','Resolved IP address for %1$s:'=>'%1$s 的解析 IP 地址：','%1$sAppearance updated.%2$s You may need to refresh the page to see some changes.'=>'%1$s外观已更新。%2$s您可能需要刷新页面才能看到部分更改。','The text entered in the "Default shortcode" field is not a valid shortcode, and was not saved.'=>'在“默认短代码”字段中输入的文本不是有效的短代码，因此未被保存。','%1$sSettings updated.%2$s You may need to refresh the page to see some changes.'=>'%1$s设置已更新。%2$s您可能需要刷新页面才能看到部分更改。','calendar event'=>'日历事件','The legacy feed request method is deprecated, and will be removed in an update in the near future. Please test your feeds with the legacy feed request method turned off.'=>'旧版数据源请求方法已被弃用，并将在近期更新中移除。请关闭旧版数据源请求方法后测试您的数据源。','Future updates of %1$s will require WordPress 5.3 or newer. Please update your site to a newer version of WordPress as soon as possible.'=>'%1$s的未来更新将要求使用WordPress 5.3或更高版本。请尽快将您的网站更新至新版WordPress。','Map'=>'地图','Recurring event'=>'再次发行','Recurs every %1$s years'=>'每%1$s年重复一次','Recurs yearly'=>'每年重复','Recurs every %1$s months'=>'每%1$s个月重复一次','Recurs monthly'=>'每月重复','Recurs every %1$s weeks'=>'每%1$s周重复一次','Recurs weekly'=>'每周重复','Recurs every %1$s days'=>'每%1$s天重复一次','Recurs daily'=>'每日重复','The "url" property in your %1$s shortcode appears to contain HTML tags; most likely your URL has been turned into a clickable link. Your calendar may not display properly as a result. Please remove the clickable link in the shortcode.'=>'您%1$s短代码中的"url"属性似乎包含HTML标签；很可能您的URL已被转换为可点击链接。这可能导致日历无法正常显示。请移除短代码中的可点击链接。','The r34ics_url_get_contents() function is no longer supported.'=>'r34ics_url_get_contents() 函数不再受支持。','Add %1$s'=>'添加%1$s','Close'=>'关闭作为','ICS Feed URL:'=>'ICS 源网址：','Be sure you are using a %1$ssubscribe%2$s URL, not a %3$sweb view%4$s URL.%5$s (Entering the URL directly in your web browser should download an %6$s file.)'=>'请确保您使用的是%1$s订阅%2$s链接，而非%3$s网页视图%4$s链接。%5$s（直接在浏览器中输入该链接应能下载%6$s文件。）','Calendar Title:'=>'日历标题：','Leave empty to use calendar&rsquo;s default title. Enter %1$s to omit title altogether.'=>'留空则使用日历默认标题。输入%1$s则完全省略标题。','Calendar Description:'=>'日历说明：','Leave empty to use calendar&rsquo;s default description. Enter %1$s to omit description altogether.'=>'留空使用日历的默认描述。输入%1$s则完全省略描述。','View:'=>'视图：','month'=>'月','list'=>'列表','week'=>'周','Count:'=>'计数：','Format:'=>'格式：','Leave %1$s blank to include all upcoming events. %2$s must be a standard %3$sPHP date format string%4$s.'=>'留空%1$s表示包含所有即将发生的事件。%2$s必须为标准%3$sPHP日期格式字符串%4$s。','Show event descriptions %1$s(change to a number in inserted shortcode to set word limit)%2$s'=>'显示活动描述 %1$s(在插入的短代码中将数字替换为字数限制)%2$s','Show event locations %1$s(if available)%2$s'=>'显示活动地点 %1$s(如有可用)%2$s','Show event organizers %1$s(if available)%2$s'=>'显示活动组织者%1$s(如有可用)%2$s','%1$sNote:%2$s Additional %3$sdisplay options%4$s are available by manually editing the shortcode after insertion.'=>'%1$s注：%2$s 插入后可通过手动编辑短代码获取更多%3$s显示选项%4$s。','Insert %1$s'=>'插入 %1$s','Do even more with %1$s version 6!'=>'%1$s 版本 6 让您事半功倍！','Calendar Builder + Block Editor'=>'日历生成器 + 区块编辑器','Configure all calendar settings with an easy visual interface, and use the new %1$s block to select your saved calendars from a dropdown in the Block Editor, no shortcode needed! %2$sLearn more...%3$s'=>'通过简洁的可视化界面配置所有日历设置，并使用全新的%1$s代码块，在代码块编辑器中从下拉菜单选择已保存的日历——无需短代码！%2$s了解更多...%3$s','Additional Views and Enhanced Features'=>'附加视图与增强功能','%1$s offers many new ways to display your calendar, including integrations with the popular %2$s and %3$s open source libraries. Month and year views with a sidebar for the selected day. "Up Next" works great for radio or TV station schedules. Widget and year availability are perfect for holiday bookings. Plus, additional capabilities are added to the core Month, Basic, List and Week views. %4$sView sample calendars...%5$s'=>'%1$s 提供了多种全新的日历展示方式，包括与流行的%2$s和%3$s开源库的集成。月视图和年视图均配备侧边栏，可显示选定日期。 "即将上演"功能特别适合广播电台或电视台节目安排。小工具和年度视图功能完美适用于假期预订。此外，核心的月视图、基础视图、列表视图和周视图均新增了更多功能。%4$s查看示例日历...%5$s','Customization'=>'定制','Easy-to-use tools to completely customize your calendar colors, typography and more. Select one of our preset color palettes or create your own, with options to individually customize the color of each element in the calendar layout. Choose between your theme fonts, system fonts, or more than 20 included open source fonts. %1$sLearn more...%2$s'=>'易于使用的工具，可完全自定义日历的颜色、字体排版等元素。选择我们预设的配色方案，或创建专属配色，支持逐项调整日历布局中每个元素的颜色。字体选择涵盖主题字体、系统字体以及内置的20余种开源字体。%1$s了解更多...%2$s','ICS Events'=>'ICS活动','Turns %1$s into a full calendar management system. Create and edit new events directly in WordPress, and even integrate them seamlessly with your existing external ICS feeds. %2$sLearn more...%3$s'=>'将%1$s转化为完整的日历管理系统。直接在WordPress中创建和编辑新事件，甚至能与您现有的外部ICS源无缝集成。%2$s了解更多...%3$s','Localized Admin Interface'=>'本地化管理界面','All %1$s admin pages are translated into dozens of languages, including English, Czech, Danish, German, Greek, Spanish, Estonian, Finnish, French, Hungarian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Lithuanian, Latvian, Norwegian, Dutch, Polish, Portuguese, Romanian, Russian, Slovak, Serbian, Swedish, Turkish, Ukrainian, and Chinese.'=>'所有%1$s管理页面均已翻译成数十种语言，包括英语、捷克语、丹麦语、德语、希腊语、西班牙语、爱沙尼亚语、芬兰语、法语、匈牙利语、意大利语、日语、韩语、立陶宛语、拉脱维亚语、挪威语、荷兰语、波兰语、葡萄牙语、罗马尼亚语、俄语、斯洛伐克语、塞尔维亚语、瑞典语、土耳其语、乌克兰语和中文。','Visit %1$s to learn more.'=>'访问 %1$s 了解更多。','Calendar Builder screenshot'=>'日历生成器截图','Appearance screenshot'=>'外观截图','Available now!'=>'现已上市！','Get %1$s!'=>'获取%1$s！','Extensive color palette and typography options are available with %1$s. %2$sLearn More%3$s'=>'提供丰富的配色方案和排版选项，详情请见%1$s。%2$s了解更多%3$s','Color Palette'=>'调色板','Match calendar color palette to current Block Theme colors'=>'将日历配色方案匹配为当前区块主题的颜色','beta'=>'公测','Replaces the %1$s default neutral color palette with nearest matches from the current Site Editor Styles color palette or the %2$s file in your theme. Color selections are algorithmic, and some combinations may not pass accessibility contrast tests. This setting has no effect if you are using a "classic" theme that does not include a %3$s file.'=>'将默认中性色板%1$s替换为当前站点编辑器样式色板或主题内%2$s文件中最接近的匹配色。颜色选择采用算法生成，部分组合可能无法通过无障碍对比度测试。若使用未包含%3$s文件的"经典"主题，此设置将无效。','%1$sThis is currently a beta feature.%2$s It may require making some adjustments to your calendar appearance or CSS for optimal display, especially if you have color-coded your feeds. Functionality is subject to change.'=>'%1$s此功能目前处于测试阶段。%2$s为获得最佳显示效果，可能需要调整日历外观或CSS样式，尤其当您为订阅源设置了颜色标记时。功能可能随时变更。','Dark mode'=>'黑暗模式','Inverts color palette (light colors on a dark background).'=>'反转配色方案（浅色系配深色背景）。','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','Thank you for installing %1$s. Before creating your first calendar shortcode, please visit your %2$sGeneral Settings%3$s page and verify that your site language, timezone and date/time format settings are correct. See our %4$sUser Guide%5$s for more information.'=>'感谢您安装%1$s。在创建首个日历短代码前，请访问您的%2$s常规设置%3$s页面，确认网站语言、时区及日期/时间格式设置是否正确。更多信息请参阅我们的%4$s用户指南%5$s。','Get started with %1$s in four easy steps... and you\'ve already completed step one! Check out our %2$sQuick Start Guide%3$s for the rest.'=>'只需四个简单步骤即可开始使用%1$s...而您已经完成了第一步！请查阅我们的%2$s快速入门指南%3$s了解后续步骤。','Quick Start Guide'=>'快速指导','An extensive %1$sUser Guide%2$s is available on our website. Below are some quick links to key resources in the documentation.'=>'我们的网站上提供了一份详尽的%1$s用户指南%2$s。以下是文档中关键资源的快速链接：','General:'=>'常规：','General WordPress Settings'=>'WordPress 常规设置','%1$s Settings'=>'%1$s 设置','Working with Shortcodes:'=>'使用简码','Shortcode Overview'=>'短代码概述','Shortcode Builder'=>'短码生成器','Shortcode Parameters Reference'=>'短代码参数参考','Advanced Topics:'=>'进阶主题：','FAQs and Tips'=>'常见问题与技巧','CSS Guide'=>'CSS指南','Developer Resources'=>'开发人员资源','GDPR'=>'GDPR','Loading'=>'载入中','Always use AJAX to render calendars'=>'始终使用AJAX来渲染日历','AJAX loading is now automatic. You can override AJAX, if necessary, by adding %1$s to your shortcode.'=>'AJAX加载现已自动进行。如有必要，您可通过在短代码后添加%1$s来覆盖AJAX功能。','Increase memory limit when rendering calendars'=>'渲染日历时增加内存限制','If your calendar is failing to load with an "out of memory" fatal error, try increasing the memory limit. A minimum of 512 MB is recommended. %1$s Notes: 1) Some hosting providers may not allow applications to override the server default setting. 2) It is not possible to set this option lower than the current default memory limit on your server.'=>'若日历加载时出现"内存不足"致命错误，请尝试提高内存限制。建议最低设置为512 MB。%1$s注意事项：1) 部分主机服务商可能不允许应用程序覆盖服务器默认设置。2) 此选项无法设置为低于服务器当前默认内存限制的值。','deprecated'=>'禁用','Some servers may not support the default feed request method. If your feeds are not loading, turn on this option to use the legacy request method. This feature is deprecated and will be removed in a future update.'=>'某些服务器可能不支持默认的订阅源请求方式。若您的订阅源无法加载，请启用此选项以使用传统请求方式。该功能已被弃用，将在未来更新中移除。','Default shortcode'=>'默认短代码','If your site will include a large number of similarly configured calendar shortcodes, you can enter a default "base" shortcode here with the parameters that should be the same for all of the calendars. Individual shortcodes on the site can then include only the parameters that are unique to that calendar, as such: %1$s Any parameters included in the individual shortcode will override what is set here.'=>'若您的网站将包含大量配置相似的日历短代码，可在此处输入默认的"基础"短代码，其中参数需适用于所有日历。网站上的独立短代码只需包含该日历特有的参数，例如：%1$s 独立短代码中包含的任何参数都将覆盖此处设置的值。','Allow access to these hostnames that resolve to reserved IP addresses'=>'允许访问这些解析为保留IP地址的主机名','If your calendar server is hosted on the same physical server as your website, is part of the same local network, or otherwise uses a %1$sreserved IP address%2$s, enter its hostname here to allow access. For multiple calendar servers, enter one hostname per line. See %3$sthe %4$s documentation%5$s for more information.'=>'如果您的日历服务器与网站托管在同一台物理服务器上、属于同一局域网，或使用了%1$s保留IP地址%2$s，请在此处输入其主机名以允许访问。若存在多个日历服务器，请每行输入一个主机名。更多信息请参阅%3$s相关%4$s文档%5$s。','Enter one hostname per line. Hostnames are the base domain name, not a full URL. %1$s For example, you would enter %2$s, not %3$s.'=>'每行输入一个主机名。主机名应为基础域名，而非完整URL。%1$s 例如，应输入%2$s而非%3$s。','Allow access to these ports'=>'允许访问这些端口','WordPress automatically allows access to ports 80, 443, and 8080. If you need to be able to access source calendars that use non-standard ports, enter the port numbers here, separated by commas.'=>'WordPress 默认允许访问 80、443 和 8080 这三个端口。若需访问使用非标准端口的源日历，请在此处输入端口号，用逗号分隔。','Caching'=>'缓存','Transient (cache) expiration'=>'临时（缓存）过期','seconds'=>'秒','Sets how long calendar feed data should be cached on the server (WordPress transients) before reloading. Default is 3600 (1 hour). Minimum allowed value is 120 (2 minutes).'=>'设置日历源数据在服务器（WordPress 暂存数据）中缓存的时间长度，之后将重新加载。默认值为 3600（1 小时）。允许的最小值为 120（2 分钟）。','Admin'=>'管理','Minimum access role'=>'最低访问角色','Identifies the minimum user role that is allowed to access %1$s admin pages. Certain areas such as Settings are further restricted to %2$s users only (%3$s users on Multisite configurations).'=>'确定允许访问%1$s管理页面的最低用户角色。某些区域（如设置）进一步限制为仅限%2$s用户访问（在多站点配置中为%3$s用户）。','Register Customizer'=>'注册自定义程序','WordPress no longer includes a link to the Customizer in the Appearance menu when a Block Theme is active. Check this box if you wish to use the Customizer, e.g. for the Additional CSS input. Note: Some themes or plugins may already register the Customizer, in which case, this setting will have no effect. (The checkbox only enables the Customizer when checked; it does not disable the Customizer when unchecked.'=>'当启用区块主题时，WordPress 不会在“外观”菜单中显示自定义工具的链接。若需使用自定义工具（例如输入附加 CSS），请勾选此复选框。注意：某些主题或插件可能已注册自定义工具，此时此设置将无效。（该复选框仅在勾选时启用自定义工具，取消勾选不会禁用该功能。）','Remove "Add ICS Calendar" button in Classic Editor'=>'在经典编辑器中移除“添加ICS日历”按钮','By default, ICS Calendar adds an "Add ICS Calendar" button to the toolbar above the WYSIWYG editor when using Classic Editor. Check this box to remove the button. Has no effect on sites using the Block Editor (Gutenberg).'=>'默认情况下，当使用经典编辑器时，ICS日历会在所见即所得编辑器上方的工具栏中添加一个"添加ICS日历"按钮。勾选此框可移除该按钮。此设置对使用块编辑器（古腾堡）的网站无效。','%1$s version 10.6 introduced new default values for several shortcode parameters. New installations automatically use the new default values, but upgraded installations will continue to use the old default values, unless this box is checked. Read more about these changes on %2$sour blog%3$s.'=>'%1$s 版本 10.6 为若干短代码参数引入了新的默认值。新安装的系统将自动采用新默认值，但升级后的系统将继续使用旧默认值，除非勾选此选项框。更多变更详情请参阅%2$s我们的博客%3$s。','User Guide'=>'用户指南','Our complete user guide is available with full translation into dozens of languages on our website:'=>'我们的完整用户指南已提供数十种语言的完整翻译版本，可在我们的网站上获取：','For assistance, please use our %1$ssupport request form%2$s.'=>'如需协助，请使用我们的%1$s支持请求表单%2$s。','When contacting support, please include the %1$ssystem report%2$s from this page.'=>'联系客服时，请附上本页面的%1$s系统报告%2$s。','Spread the word!'=>'传播信息！','If you find %1$s useful, you can help support our continued growth and development with a %2$sfive-star review%3$s. Thank you!'=>'若您觉得%1$s有帮助，欢迎通过%2$s五星好评%3$s支持我们持续成长与发展。感谢您！','Calendar Status: %1$sPaused%2$s'=>'日历状态：%1$s暂停%2$s','Calendar Status: %1$sActive%2$s'=>'日历状态：%1$s活动%2$s','Use the pause button if you need to temporarily turn off %1$s on your front end pages.'=>'若需在前端页面暂时关闭%1$s功能，请使用暂停按钮。','Resume Calendars'=>'简历日历','Pause Calendars'=>'暂停日历','No content will be altered, but your calendars will be hidden and no %1$s asset files (JavaScript, CSS) will be loaded on front-end pages. If you are using caching via a plugin or through your hosting provider, you may need to clear the cache after changing this setting.'=>'内容不会被修改，但您的日历将被隐藏，且前端页面不会加载任何%1$s资源文件（JavaScript、CSS）。若您通过插件或主机服务商启用了缓存功能，修改此设置后可能需要清除缓存。','%1$s Data Cache'=>'%1$s 数据缓存','This will immediately clear all existing cached calendar data (purge transients), forcing WordPress to reload all calendars the next time they are viewed. Caching will then resume as before.'=>'这将立即清除所有现有的缓存日历数据（清除临时数据），迫使WordPress在下次查看时重新加载所有日历。缓存功能随后将恢复如常。','Clear Cached Calendar Data'=>'清除缓存的日历数据','If you are using a third-party caching plugin, you may need to clear your site-wide cache after running this utility.'=>'若您使用的是第三方缓存插件，运行此工具后可能需要清除全站缓存。','Are you sure? This will reset all %1$s settings to their defaults. Your saved calendar configurations and shortcodes will be retained, but resetting the defaults may change the appearance of your calendars. If you are using a third-party caching plugin, you may need to clear your site-wide cache after running this utility.'=>'确定吗？这将把所有 %1$s 设置重置为默认值。您保存的日历配置和简码将被保留，但重置默认值可能会改变日历的外观。如果您使用第三方缓存插件，可能需要在运行此实用程序后清除全站缓存。','Only clear transients (default)'=>'仅清晰瞬态（默认）','Also clear all saved ICS feed URLs'=>'同时清除所有已保存的ICS源URL','Reset %1$sall%2$s %3$s settings (including transients and feed URLs)'=>'重置%1$s所有%2$s %3$s设置（包括临时数据和订阅源网址）','Last cleared:'=>'最后一次清理：','never'=>'从不','ICS Feed URL Tester'=>'ICS 源网址测试工具','If you are concerned that the plugin is not properly retrieving your feed, you can test the URL here.'=>'若您担心插件未能正确获取您的订阅源，可在此处测试该URL。','Enter feed URL...'=>'输入订阅源网址...','Test URL'=>'测试网址','Results:'=>'结果：','%1$s received.'=>'%1$s 已收到。','This appears to be a valid ICS feed URL.'=>'这似乎是一个有效的ICS源URL。','unknown'=>'未知','This does not appear to be a valid ICS feed URL.'=>'这似乎不是一个有效的ICS源URL。','Could not retrieve data from the requested URL.'=>'无法从请求的URL获取数据。','An unknown error occurred while attempting to retrieve the requested URL.'=>'在尝试获取请求的URL时发生未知错误。','Please copy the following text and include it in your message when emailing support.'=>'请复制以下文本，并在发送支持邮件时将其包含在您的消息中。','Also please include the %1$s shortcode exactly as you have it entered on the affected page.'=>'请务必包含%1$s短代码，且必须与您在受影响页面中输入的完全一致。','No events found.'=>'没有发现活动事件。','Previous Page'=>'上一页','Next Page'=>'下一页','All Day'=>'全天','Previous Month'=>'上月','Next Month'=>'下个月','Today'=>'今天','Month selection'=>'月份选择','No events.'=>'没有事件。','No additional events this month.'=>'本月没有其他活动。','Week selection'=>'周数选择','Last week'=>'上周','This week'=>'本周','Next week'=>'下周','ICS Calendar'=>'ICS 日历','https://icscalendar.com'=>'https://icscalendar.com','Turn your Google Calendar, Microsoft Office 365 or Apple iCloud Calendar into a seamlessly integrated, auto-updating, zero-maintenance WordPress experience.'=>'将您的谷歌日历、微软Office 365或苹果iCloud日历转化为无缝集成、自动更新且零维护的WordPress体验。','Room 34 Creative Services, LLC'=>'Room 34 Creative Services, LLC']];
